title: Looking for a group to play with
body: Hey people, just wondering if any of you have a discord or teamspeak group that you guys play with that you wouldnt mind sharing? Looking for some chill lads to play some games with!

replies.body: hey going buddy i have both and what rank players you looking for as im silver 3
Any rank is fine, just a teamspeak with friendly dudes is good enough for me. :)
